    "body" : "<p>Yep - 'E' does the trick</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://download.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/text/SimpleDateFormat.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">http://download.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/text/SimpleDateFormat.html</a></p>\n\n<pre><code>Date date = new Date();\nDateFormat df = new SimpleDateFormat(\"yyyy-MM-E\");\nSystem.out.println(df.format(date));\n</code></pre>\n"
